  m_Name: The Deluge
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::Seed
  title: The Deluge
  description: "Pontiff, urgent news! The tears of the Beholder have been falling
    without cease for the past few days, and the city\u2019s sewers can no longer
    contain the flow. The people are whispering of a coming flood! We could mobilize
    the faithful to protect our temples, for if they are damaged, restoring them
    will cost a fortune. Yet, we cannot simply abandon the common folk, can we?"
